This is an 8 Puzzle game written in Python using Pygame.
There are 9 tiles in a 3x3 square out which space for one tile is left empty.
The player has to slide the tiles into that empty block and the game ends when the tiles are arranged in an increasing order.

Requirement:
            Pygame
            
